You respond 2\D, a 2/1 force to game.  Partner rebids 2\h, showing a 4-card side suit.

You don't have 4 \Hs, nor do you have have 3 \Ss. You do, however, have stoppers in \Cs so you bid 2NT. 
North happily says 3NT.}

